## Before Production Auth

- [ ] Set up custom domain (`mtamta.com` + `api.mtamta.com`) — refresh cookie is `SameSite=Lax`, which requires same root domain between web and API. Won't work on `.pages.dev` / `.railway.app` split.
- [ ] Run migration `002_email_normalize` on production Postgres
- [ ] PATCH /users/me cannot clear nullable fields (`bio`, `avatar_url`) — COALESCE treats null same as omitted. Fix when building profile UI (Phase 6).

